import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';

function GridBasicExample() {
  return (
    <Form>
      <Row>
        <Col>
            <Form.Range 
                label="Select # of samples to use"
                step={10}
                min={0}
                max={100}
            />

        </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col>
            <Form.Check 
                type="switch"
                id="task1-switch"
                label="Task1"
            />
        </Col>
        <Col>
            <Form.Check 
                type="switch"
                id="task2-switch"
                label="Task2"
            />
        </Col>
        <Col>
            <Form.Check 
                type="switch"
                id="task3-switch"
                label="Task3"
            />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default GridBasicExample;
